'''淚血症'''（{{lang-en|'''Haemolacria'''}}）是身體的一種現象，指眼睛因為不明原因而排出含部分[[血液|血液]]的[[淚水|淚水]]。這可能是多種疾病的病徵<ref name="Ahluwalia">{{cite journal | last=Ahluwalia | first=BK | coauthors=Khurana AK, Sood S | title=Bloody tears (haemolacria) | journal=Indian Journal of Ophthalmology | volume=35 | issue=1 | pages=41–43 | url=http://www.ijo.in/article.asp?issn=0301-4738;year=1987;volume=35;issue=1;spage=41;epage=43;aulast=Ahluwalia | pmid=3450614 | language=en | date=Jan–Feb 1987 | access-date=2013-07-04 | archive-date=2021-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309152555/https://www.ijo.in/article.asp?issn=0301-4738;year=1987;volume=35;issue=1;spage=41;epage=43;aulast=Ahluwalia | dead-url=no }}</ref>，也有可能是[[淚器|淚器]]有[[腫瘤|腫瘤]]的現象。最常見的可能，是[[細菌性結膜炎|細菌]]、環境破壞或損傷引致的[[結膜炎|結膜炎]]引起<ref name="pmid1750328">{{cite journal |author=Ottovay E, Norn M |title=Occult haemolacria in females |journal=[[Acta_Ophthalmol_(Copenh)|Acta Ophthalmol (Copenh)]] |volume=69 |issue=4 |pages=544–6 |pmid=1750328 |doi= 10.1111/j.1755-3768.1991.tb02038.x|url= |date=August 1991}}</ref>。

生育婦女亦有可能會出現一種急性的淚血症，那是一種由於[[荷爾蒙|荷爾蒙]]引起<ref name="pmid1750328"/>的病變，就好像[[子宮內膜移位|子宮內膜移位]]引致的身體出血現象。

==已知案例==
===智利女生歐利瓦===
來自[[智利|智利]]的一名20歲女生歐利瓦（{{lang|es|Yaritza Oliva}}）是最新近的一位淚血症患者<ref>{{cite news |title=智利「血淚女孩」　正妹疑罹患罕見淚血症 |publisher=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]]新奇新聞 |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130629/233864.htm |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2013-07-12 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307233424/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130629/233864.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Youtube |id=g5AQYhPkGFk |title=Chilean Woman Cries Tears of Blood |author=Gary Parkosweich |language=en }}</ref>，2013年6月開始得病。現時只依靠醫生開出的眼藥水去舒緩病情。
===印度女生特文科尔·德维韦迪===
來自[[印度|印度]][[北方邦|北方邦]]首府[[勒克瑙|勒克瑙]]的特文科尔·德维韦迪（{{lang|en|Twinkle Dwivedi}}）也有淚血症，不過有英國醫生指她的病因有可能是由[[冯维勒布兰德氏病|冯维勒布兰德氏病]]引起<ref name=39net /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/32797753|title=Doctor probes mystery of girl who cries blood|date=09-11-2009|accessdate=2010-04-29|work=MSNBC Today|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115143709/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/32797753|archive-date=2010-01-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。特文科尔成為多項醫學研究的對象，也在多個電視節目如《[[BodyShock|BodyShock]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channel4.com/programmes/bodyshock/episode-guide/series-20/episode-1|title=Girl Who Cries Blood|accessdate=2010-04-29|work=Bodyshock|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061936/http://www.channel4.com/programmes/bodyshock/episode-guide/series-20/episode-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>及《[[國家地理頻道|國家地理頻道]]》的紀錄片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ngccommunity.nationalgeographic.com/ngcblogs/inside-ngc/2009/09/filming-the-girl-who-cries-blood.html |title=Filming "The Girl Who Cries Blood" |accessdate=2010-04-29 |work=National Geographic |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413230522/http://ngccommunity.nationalgeographic.com/ngcblogs/inside-ngc/2009/09/filming-the-girl-who-cries-blood.html |archivedate=2010-04-13 }}</ref>出現。

由於她的病況缺乏醫學解釋，故有不少人提出在宗教上的可能解釋。她亦有可能是得到了一種到現在我們還未知道的疾病，但由於現時只有她一個患者，所以無法對此病作出更深入的研究。但更多懷疑者假設她的病況其實可以用[[孟喬森症候群|代理型孟喬森症候群]]來解釋，也就是說其實是一種[[人為疾患|人為疾患]]：作為特文科尔開始流血的唯一目擊者，她的母親很可能是整件事的始作俑者，原先只是構想出一個故事，卻無意中引發特文科爾的病況出來<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/last-nights-television--muslim-driving-school-bbc2-girl-who-cries-blood-channel-4-the-man-who-couldnt-stop-hiccuping-bbc1-1865840.html|title=Last Night's Television - Muslim Driving School, BBC2; Girl Who Cries Blood, Channel 4; The Man Who Couldn't Stop Hiccuping, BBC1|date=2010-01-13|accessdate=2010-04-29|work=The Independent UK|location=London|first=Tom|last=Sutcliffe|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925023210/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/last-nights-television--muslim-driving-school-bbc2-girl-who-cries-blood-channel-4-the-man-who-couldnt-stop-hiccuping-bbc1-1865840.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===美國男生卡尔维诺·英曼===
來自[[美國|美國]][[田納西州|田納西州]]{{link-en|罗克伍德|Rockwood}}的卡尔维诺·英曼（{{lang|en|Calvino Inman}}）在2009年15歲時得到淚血症，每天淚血三次<ref>{{cite news |url=http://g1.globo.com/Noticias/Ciencia/0,,MUL1291894-5603,00-ADOLESCENTE+AMERICANO+CHORA+SANGUE+ATE+TRES+VEZES+POR+DIA+DIZ+SITE.html |title=Adolescente americano chora sangue até três vezes por dia, diz site |language=pt |accessdate=2013-07-04 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809180330/http://g1.globo.com/Noticias/Ciencia/0,,MUL1291894-5603,00-ADOLESCENTE+AMERICANO+CHORA+SANGUE+ATE+TRES+VEZES+POR+DIA+DIZ+SITE.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，原因未明。但由於他住在傳統被視為保守的「[[聖經帶|聖經地帶]]」，因而被朋友視為「魔鬼附身」<ref name=39net>{{cite news |url=http://news.39.net/qwqs/099/4/985596.html |title=少年眼中泪血 被指魔鬼附身 |publisher=39健康新聞 |date=2009-09-04 |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2013-07-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072656/http://news.39.net/qwqs/099/4/985596.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===印度女生拉西达===
來自[[印度|印度]][[巴特那市|巴特那市]]的拉西达（{{lang|en|Rashida Khatoon}}）亦在2009年得到淚血症，每天淚血五次，而且有時在流過淚血之後會暈倒<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.weirdasianews.com/2009/05/13/indian-girl-cries-tears-blood |title=Indian girl cries tears blood |language=en |date=2009-05-13 |accessdate=2013-07-04 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127184633/https://www.weirdasianews.com/2009/05/13/indian-girl-cries-tears-blood/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

